window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Cinda Williams Chima won accolades for her <i>New York Times</i> best-selling Heir trilogy. The first of a new young-adult trilogy, <i>The Demon King</i> features a former thief, Han, who’s trying to provide for his mother and sister. One day Han, who sports mysterious (and certainly magical) silver cuffs on his wrists, confronts wizards setting fire to a sacred mountain. Now possessing one ofthe wizards’ amulets, Han faces more trouble than he ever could have imagined.</p>"; 
